9#include "ipf.h"
10
11
12void
13printunit(unit)
14 int unit;
15{
16
17 switch (unit)
18 {
19 case IPL_LOGIPF :
20 PRINTF("ipf");
21 break;
22 case IPL_LOGNAT :
23 PRINTF("nat");
24 break;
25 case IPL_LOGSTATE :
26 PRINTF("state");
27 break;
28 case IPL_LOGAUTH :
29 PRINTF("auth");
30 break;
31 case IPL_LOGSYNC :
32 PRINTF("sync");
33 break;
34 case IPL_LOGSCAN :
35 PRINTF("scan");
36 break;
37 case IPL_LOGLOOKUP :
38 PRINTF("lookup");
39 break;
40 case IPL_LOGCOUNT :
41 PRINTF("count");
42 break;
43 case IPL_LOGALL :
44 PRINTF("all");
45 break;
46 default :
47 PRINTF("unknown(%d)", unit);
48 }
49}
